summary: The author is currently enrolled in a Bachelor of Science degree program in Physical Education/Sports Management at Towson State University in Maryland. The author also volunteers as a part-time Aerobics Instructor at Bally's Holiday Spa in Baltimore, Maryland, and is a volunteer for the March of Dimes. He is the author of the book ‘CURRICULUM VITAE’.
